title: Android Irc Biff wiggle
description:
Android's most advanced IRC client.
Android IRC is the Premier Android Internet Relay Chat Client. Worlds better than the rest.
Supports:
* SSL
* SASL
* Multiple Servers
* Nick Completion
* Notifications
* Stays connected in background
* IRC/mIRC/ANSI Colors
* User List
* Supports BNCs (tested ZNC and PsyBNC)
* Individual Windows for Messages and Channels
* Timestamps
* Volume Keys Change Font Size

this cannot be updated via the android market
